## AI Pipeline Trigger & Optimisation

### Trigger
â€¢ The full AI pipeline (Clause Extraction, Risk Detection, Embedding/RAG index, Diff Summary) executes **every time a new file version is saved**, whether it is v1, v2, or later.

### Optimisation rules
1. Clause Extraction and Risk Detection always re-run, but pages whose text hash is identical to the previous version are skipped to save tokens.  
2. Embeddings are cached by exact text hash; unchanged chunks are reused at zero cost.  
3. Diff Summary is generated only when a prior locked version exists.

### Cost & UX
â€¢ Daily soft limit: 2 000 tokens per user per contract; backend spend capped at US $5.  
â€¢ While jobs run, each AI tab shows an "AI updatingâ€¦" badge; a WebSocket `AI_READY` event refreshes the tabs automatically when processing completes.

